               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit lines of Text I alternating with black lines; initial words of sections and subsections of Text I;&#xD;
Incipit and heading of Text II; subsections indicating the day on which the new year begins; &#xD;
Three initial lines of Text III, alternating with black lines.&#xD;
Elements of punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
